deck.gl rendering with:\\n// - Task blocks rendered in MESO layer (blue, orange, red, gray)\\n// - Timeline header with dates\\n// - Sidebar with train IDs\\n// - Minimap with heatmap\\n// - FPS: 120 (avg: 119) - excellent performance!\", \"user_feedback\": \"Excellent! deck.gl is rendering correctly! The screenshot shows task blocks, timeline, sidebar, minimap - FPS 120\", \"context\": \"deck.gl canvas implementation after R3F removal - working at 120 FPS\", \"source_line\": 3290}\n{\"task_id\": \"TASK-040\", \"code_type\": \"config\", \"file_name\": \"package.json-blueprint\", \"code\": \"{\\n  \\\"dependencies\\\": {\\n    \\\"@blueprintjs/core\\\": \\\"^6.4.1\\\",\\n    \\\"@blueprintjs/icons\\\": \\\"^6.x\\\",\\n    \\\"@blueprintjs/table\\\": \\\"^6.x\\\",\\n    \\\"@blueprintjs/select\\\": \\\"^6.x\\\",\\n    \\\"@blueprintjs/datetime2\\\": \\\"^2.x\\\"\\n  }\\n}\", \"user_feedback\": \"Blueprint.js v6 migration complete - 4 commits made successfully\", \"context\": \"Blueprint.js package configuration after successful migration from Tailwind\", \"source_line\": 1524}\n{\"task_id\": \"TASK-040\", \"code_type\": \"config\", \"file_name\": \"CLAUDE.md\", \"code\": \"# MMS Development Guidelines\\n\\n## Language Policy\\n- ALL code, comments, and documentation MUST be in English only\\n- No Portuguese or other languages in any files\\n- Git commit messages in English\\n\\n## Git Workflow\\n- Commit after EVERY small step completed\\n- Use conventional commits: feat:, fix:, docs:, refactor:, test:\\n- Never batch multiple features in one commit\\n- Commit message format: type: brief description\\n\\n## Tech Stack (ZUI Architecture)\\n- Frontend: Next.js 14 + React 18 + TypeScript\\n- ZUI Engine: PixiJS (@pixi/react) for WebGL canvas rendering\\n- Charts: Apache ECharts (WebGL rendering)\\n- Gantt: Bryntum or SVAR (virtual scrolling)\\n- State: @zazcart/toolkit state-machine + TanStack Query\\n- Backend: Elysia.js (Bun runtime)\\n- Database: PostgreSQL 16 with JSONB\\n- Optimization: glpk.js (server) / YALPS (client)\\n\\n## Development Standards\\n- TypeScript strict mode\\n- ESLint + Prettier for formatting\\n- Canvas/WebGL for > 1000 elements\\n- SVG only for < 1000 interactive elements\\n- Virtual scrolling for lists > 100 items\\n- 60 FPS minimum for animations\", \"user_feedback\": \"CLAUDE.md created with development guidelines\", \"context\": \"Development guidelines document for AI-assisted development\", \"source_line\": 1532}\n{\"task_id\": \"TASK-040\", \"code_type\": \"style\", \"file_name\": \"design-tokens-light\", \"code\": \":root {\\n  /* Brand Colors */\\n  --mms-primary: #2563eb;\\n  --mms-primary-hover: #1d4ed8;\\n  \\n  /* Background Colors */\\n  --mms-bg-app: #f8fafc;\\n  --mms-bg-card: #ffffff;\\n  --mms-bg-surface: #f5f8fa;\\n  \\n  /* Text Colors */\\n  --mms-text-primary: #182026;\\n  --mms-text-secondary: #5c7080;\\n  --mms-text-muted: #8a9ba8;\\n  \\n  /* Status Colors */\\n  --mms-status-available: #22c55e;\\n  --mms-status-in-service: #3b82f6;\\n  --mms-status-maintenance: #ef4444;\\n  \\n  /* Spacing Scale */\\n  --mms-space-xs: 4px;\\n  --mms-space-sm: 8px;\\n  --mms-space-md: 16px;\\n  --mms-space-lg: 24px;\\n}\", \"user_feedback\": \"Design tokens working correctly - visual testing passed all pages\", \"context\": \"CSS custom properties for light theme - later replaced by Blueprint native\", \"source_line\": 987}\n{\"task_id\": \"TASK-040\", \"code_type\": \"style\", \"file_name\": \"design-tokens-dark\", \"code\": \".bp5-dark {\\n  /* Background Colors - Dark Mode */\\n  --mms-bg-app: #1a1a2e;\\n  --mms-bg-card: #16213e;\\n  --mms-bg-surface: #1f2937;\\n  --mms-bg-hover: #374151;\\n  --mms-bg-selected: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);\\n\\n  /* Text Colors - Dark Mode */\\n  --mms-text-primary: #f9fafb;\\n  --mms-text-secondary: #d1d5db;\\n  --mms-text-muted: #9ca3af;\\n  --mms-text-disabled: #6b7280;\\n\\n  /* Border Colors - Dark Mode */\\n  --mms-border-default: #374151;\\n  --mms-border-light: #4b5563;\\n  --mms-border-focus: #3b82f6;\\n}\", \"user_feedback\": \"Dark mode working - screenshots verified on dashboard, map, schedule pages\", \"context\": \"CSS custom properties for dark mode using Blueprint bp5-dark class\", \"source_line\": 1019}\n{\"task_id\": \"TASK-040\", \"code_type\": \"component\", \"file_name\": \"FleetMap-status-colors\", \"code\": \"const statusColors: Record<TrainStatus, string> = {\\n  available: 'var(--mms-status-available)',\\n  'in-service': 'var(--mms-status-in-service)',\\n  maintenance: 'var(--mms-status-maintenance)',\\n};\", \"user_feedback\": \"Status colors using tokens verified in visual testing\", \"context\": \"Train status color mapping using design tokens\", \"source_line\": 987}\n{\"task_id\": \"TASK-040\", \"code_type\": \"component\", \"file_name\": \"maintenance-tag-colors\", \"code\": \"const MAINTENANCE_TAG_COLORS: Record<string, { bg: string; color: string }> = {\\n  PM1: { bg: 'var(--mms-maint-pm1)', color: '#ffffff' },\\n  PM2: { bg: 'var(--mms-maint-pm2)', color: '#ffffff' },\\n  HM: { bg: 'var(--mms-maint-hm)', color: '#ffffff' },\\n  OVH: { bg: 'var(--mms-maint-ovh)', color: '#ffffff' },\\n};\", \"user_feedback\": \"Maintenance type legend showing correct colors (PM1 green, PM2 blue, HM amber, OVH red)\", \"context\": \"Schedule page maintenance colors using design tokens\", \"source_line\": 987}\n{\"task_id\": \"TASK-040\", \"code_type\": \"config\", \"file_name\": \"architecture-plan\", \"code\": \"CAMADA 1: O CEREBRO (Background/Workers)\\n- Processamento de dados brutos e logica de restricoes (Constraint Deck)\\n- Calcula disponibilidade de trilhos e mao de obra em threads separadas\\n\\nCAMADA 2: O CANVAS (WebGL / PixiJS)\\n- Responsavel por 90% do conteudo visual dinamico\\n- Renderiza barras de tarefas, conexoes de dependencia e heatmaps\\n- Utiliza tecnicas de LOD (Level of Detail):\\n  * Zoom Macro (< 3 meses): Exibe Heatmap de densidade\\n  * Zoom Micro (> 1 semana): Exibe barras detalhadas com icones e status\\n\\nCAMADA 3: INTERFACE HUD (HTML/React Overlay)\\n- Camada superior transparente (pointer-events: none, exceto nos botoes)\\n- Contem:\\n  * Eixo de Tempo (Cabecalho): HTML para nitidez perfeita das datas\\n  * Lista de Trens (Lateral Esquerda): Virtual List sincronizada com scroll do Canvas\\n  * Tooltips e Menus de Contexto: Componentes React padrao\\n  * Sidebar de Cenarios e Filtros\", \"user_feedback\": \"Architecture plan approved for ZUI implementation\", \"context\": \"Three-layer architecture for high-performance rendering (Sandwich approach)\", \"source_line\": 664}\n{\"task_id\": \"TASK-040\", \"code_type\": \"config\", \"file_name\": \"semantic-zoom-levels\", \"code\": \"const useSemanticZoomLevel = (scale: number): ZoomLevel => {\\n  if (scale < 0.1) return 'decade';      // 10-year strategic\\n  if (scale < 0.25) return 'annual';\\n  if (scale < 0.5) return 'quarterly';\\n  if (scale < 1) return 'monthly';\\n  if (scale < 2) return 'weekly';\\n  return 'daily';                        // Tactical planning\\n};\", \"user_feedback\": \"Semantic zoom implementation approach accepted\", \"context\": \"Zoom level mapping for fractal view - Google Maps style\", \"source_line\": 1532}\n{\"task_id\": \"TASK-040\", \"code_type\": \"config\", \"file_name\": \"normalized-state-structure\", \"code\": \"interface NormalizedPlanningState {\\n  trains: { byId: Record<string, Train>; allIds: string[] };\\n  yearPlans: { byId: Record<string, YearPlan>; allIds: string[] };\\n  maintenanceEvents: { byId: Record<string, Event>; allIds: string[] };\\n}\\n\\ninterface ScenarioStore {\\n  scenarios: Record<string, NormalizedPlanningState>;\\n  activeScenarioId: string;\\n  comparisonScenarioIds: string[];  // Side-by-side comparison\\n}\", \"user_feedback\": \"State normalization structure approved\", \"context\": \"Normalized state for scenario management\", \"source_line\": 1532}\n{\"task_id\": \"TASK-040\", \"code_type\": \"config\", \"file_name\": \"data-aggregation-levels\", \"code\": \"| Zoom Level | Aggregation | Records per Train |\\n|------------|-------------|-------------------|\\n| Decade     | Yearly      | 10                |\\n| Annual     | Monthly     | 120               |\\n| Quarterly  | Weekly      | 520               |\\n| Daily      | Individual  | 3,650             |\\n\\nTotal for 300 trains:\\n- Decade view: 3,000 records\\n- Daily view: 1,095,000 records\\n\\nStrategy: Pre-compute aggregations server-side, fetch by viewport + buffer\", \"user_feedback\": \"Data aggregation strategy accepted for performance\", \"context\": \"Performance optimization through data aggregation at different zoom levels\", \"source_line\": 1532}\n{\"task_id\": \"TASK-040\", \"code_type\": \"config\", \"file_name\": \"tech-stack-zui\", \"code\": \"| Layer          | Technology                        | Justification                             |\\n|----------------|-----------------------------------|-------------------------------------------|\\n| ZUI Engine     | PixiJS (@pixi/react)              | WebGL performance, React integration      |\\n| Gantt          | Bryntum (enterprise) / SVAR (OSS) | Virtual scrolling, dependencies           |\\n| Charts         | Apache ECharts                    | 1M+ points, WebGL, heatmaps               |\\n| Calendar       | FullCalendar Premium              | Resource timeline, virtual scroll         |\\n| State          | @zazcart/toolkit state-machine    | Lightweight, type-safe, normalized        |\\n| Server Cache   | TanStack Query                    | Optimistic updates, caching               |\\n| Virtualization | TanStack Virtual                  | Headless, 2D grid support                 |\\n| Backend        | Elysia.js (Bun)                   | TypeBox schemas, WebSocket, TypeScript DX |\\n| Workers        | Bun Worker + Comlink              | Native TS, smol mode, pool pattern        |\\n| Optimization   | glpk.js (server) / YALPS (client) | LP/MIP solving, lightw