nt\":\"CRITICAL: Document says deck.gl but project uses R3F (React Three Fiber) + Three.js for rendering, not deck.gl directly. DESIGN_SPEC references Astro.js but project uses Vite + React 18.\",\"source_line\":3709}\n{\"task_id\":\"TASK-030\",\"finding_type\":\"context_loss\",\"content\":\"State Sync Failure: loadScenarioIntoStore function directly mutates TypedArrays but does not trigger state update notification to Zustand subscribers. Data loads but UI doesn't reflect it.\",\"source_line\":477}\n{\"task_id\":\"TASK-030\",\"finding_type\":\"visual_bug\",\"content\":\"Multiple pages have issues: Fleet page shows stub 'Train list will be implemented in Epic 3', Allocation page shows '--:--' for times and missing km values, Maintenance page shows NO maintenance blocks and all depot capacity shows 0%.\",\"source_line\":1197}\n{\"task_id\":\"TASK-030\",\"finding_type\":\"context_loss\",\"content\":\"BMAD workflow not configured for visual testing. User complaint: 'Nao esta sendo executado teste visual pelo bmad, e preciso verificar minuciosamente todas as telas - o canvas nao funciona, nada nele funciona'\",\"source_line\":1190}\n{\"task_id\":\"TASK-030\",\"finding_type\":\"wrong_package\",\"content\":\"BlueprintJS migration confusion: User had to stop AI multiple times with 'Pare! Remova todos os css customizados, devemos usar os estilos do blueprintjs'. AI kept adding custom CSS instead of using BlueprintJS properly.\",\"source_line\":1044}\n{\"task_id\":\"TASK-030\",\"finding_type\":\"context_loss\",\"content\":\"Port mismatch between Playwright and Vite: playwright.config.ts expected app on port 4321 but vite.config.ts serves on 5173. This prevented E2E tests from running correctly.\",\"source_line\":469}\n{\"task_id\":\"TASK-030\",\"finding_type\":\"context_loss\",\"content\":\"Skipped visual regression test in e2e/home.spec.ts - test.skip was used, meaning visual verification was never actually running despite being in the test file.\",\"source_line\":469}\n{\"